data.description: Enjoy this open & bright custom corner-lot gem with 9ft ceilings, newer flooring, & an inviting entry with exposed railing. This home boasts 2x6 construction on main level. All living and laundry located upstairs keeping the downstairs ready for guests and entertaining. Includes an office, bonus room over garage, XL pantry, & wider garage. Cozy up by the wood-burning fireplace. Outside, enjoy a lush yard with pomegranates, pecans, almonds and jujubes. Don't miss out on this property!
